  "texts": [
    "The results of this research have concluded that Metaverse environments make a significant contribution to the development of language skills as they allow students to learn cooperatively in social interaction and to take part in an active learning process.",
    "It can be said that it especially contributes to students' reading skills, vocabulary acquisition and listening skills.",
    "Thanks to the Metaverse-based teaching environment, students can participate in the learning process whenever they want, study collaboratively with their friends, have the opportunity to repeat as much as they want, and at the same time, they eliminate the passive role they once had in conventional distance learning.",
    "Therefore, it can be said that Metaverse-powered learning environments contribute to the effectiveness of a flipped class offering a more student-centered learning environment.",
    "Thus, the students had a chance to learn about the course outcomes with effective teaching methods before class, which allowed them to practice more during the lesson and helped them use high-level intellectual skills and learn more permanently."
  ],
